58
00:04:09,514 --> 00:04:10,605
This is me, Moo.

59
00:04:10,605 --> 00:04:13,425
An ordinary guy who dreams of becoming an idol.

60
00:04:13,425 --> 00:04:17,880
Clearly, the journey to my dream
is no bed of roses.

61
00:04:17,880 --> 00:04:20,620
It's a bed of thorns.

62
00:04:21,230 --> 00:04:24,650
For as long as I can remember, I've loved dancing.

63
00:04:24,650 --> 00:04:29,560
I got my inspiration from being on stage
and seeing the audience clap for me.

64
00:04:29,560 --> 00:04:33,252
I discovered my dream in life.
My dream is to dance.

65
00:04:33,252 --> 00:04:36,340
You think I'm the center of attention?

66
00:04:36,340 --> 00:04:38,804
I'm just an extra dancer.

67
00:04:42,170 --> 00:04:46,853
Something always gets in the way
of reaching my dream.

68
00:04:46,853 --> 00:04:51,326
But wait and see, this time I'll make it happen.

69
00:05:01,090 --> 00:05:03,655
I'm hearing back so quickly. I definitely passed.

70
00:05:07,560 --> 00:05:08,919
[You did not pass the contest.]
What the hell?

71
00:05:08,919 --> 00:05:11,325
