75
00:05:25,886 --> 00:05:29,884
I went to tutoring classes after the exam.

76
00:05:29,884 --> 00:05:31,628
Many subjects.

77
00:05:31,628 --> 00:05:34,887
Are you sure you went to tutoring classes?

78
00:05:34,887 --> 00:05:36,001
Yes.

79
00:05:36,001 --> 00:05:37,523
Give it to me.

80
00:05:38,240 --> 00:05:39,760
Give me your backpack.

81
00:05:39,760 --> 00:05:41,861
Mom.

82
