151
00:10:06,370 --> 00:10:08,118
Okay, philanthropist.

152
00:10:08,118 --> 00:10:10,818
Go and wash the vegetables before I smack you.

153
00:10:10,818 --> 00:10:12,058
Yes, Mom.

154
00:10:12,058 --> 00:10:13,702
Can you manage?

155
00:10:13,702 --> 00:10:15,376
Yes.

156
00:10:15,376 --> 00:10:17,020
Smack me.

157
00:10:24,573 --> 00:10:26,123
Is that ready?

158
00:10:44,000 --> 00:10:46,517
- I'll be back.
- Okay.

159
00:10:53,072 --> 00:10:54,664
Here's your food, Uncle Auan.

160
00:10:54,664 --> 00:10:58,120
And please let your daughter
eat this for nourishment.

161
00:10:58,120 --> 00:10:59,662
I prepared it especially for her.

162
00:10:59,662 --> 00:11:01,201
Thank you, Mr. Kang.

163
00:11:02,712 --> 00:11:05,010
- Hey, Kang.
- Hey, Neth.

164
00:11:05,010 --> 00:11:06,451
Hello, Miss Neth.

165
00:11:06,451 --> 00:11:08,097
Hi, Uncle Auan.

166
00:11:08,097 --> 00:11:09,926
