173
00:11:29,855 --> 00:11:31,080
It's fine.

174
00:11:31,080 --> 00:11:33,586
It's no big deal. My family happens to be rich.

175
00:11:33,586 --> 00:11:35,280
Okay, rich kid.

176
00:11:35,280 --> 00:11:37,300
You give him one meal a day which costs 40 baht.

177
00:11:37,300 --> 00:11:39,527
The total per month is 1200 baht.
That's not a small amount of money.

178
00:11:39,527 --> 00:11:43,302
It's only 40 baht to make the world a nicer place.
It's worth it.

179
00:11:43,302 --> 00:11:44,894
How noble you are.

180
00:11:44,894 --> 00:11:46,853
Of course, I am.

181
00:11:46,853 --> 00:11:48,345
What's wrong with you?

182
00:12:04,843 --> 00:12:07,855
Mom, is this really Nakhon Pathom?

183
00:12:07,855 --> 00:12:11,767
I haven't seen Phra Pathom Chedi.
We didn't pass Jae Kaek's either.

184
00:12:13,195 --> 00:12:18,630
You said we'd arrive in no time,
but you'd been speeding for three hours.

185
00:12:18,630 --> 00:12:20,388
This is the right place.

186
00:12:20,388 --> 00:12:24,500
You'll be far away from all the city distractions
and only focus on your studies.

187
00:12:47,638 --> 00:12:49,966
Are you sure there's a school around here?

188
00:12:49,966 --> 00:12:53,079
Yes. It's not far. You can walk there.

189
00:12:53,079 --> 00:12:55,328
Just head that way.

190
00:12:56,278 --> 00:12:57,337
That way?

191
00:12:57,337 --> 00:12:58,891
Yes.

192
00:12:58,891 --> 00:13:00,891
Are you sure you're not punishing me too harshly?

193
00:13:00,891 --> 00:13:04,559
Harshly? I chose what's best for you.

194
00:13:04,559 --> 00:13:07,069
I went to this school too back in the day.

195
00:13:07,069 --> 00:13:10,526
I graduated and became quite successful.

196
00:13:10,526 --> 00:13:12,526
I walked to school.

197
00:13:12,526 --> 00:13:17,055
While walking, I recited vocabulary
and the periodic table.

198
00:13:17,055 --> 00:13:19,064
It was so good.

199
00:13:19,064 --> 00:13:23,578
Don't make that face.
Nowadays is so much better than back then.

200
00:13:23,578 --> 00:13:30,512
When I booked the dorm, the owner said
a convenience store was only a 20-minute walk.

201
00:13:30,512 --> 00:13:33,900
Back in my days, it took me an hour
to go shopping in the city.

202
00:13:34,570 --> 00:13:35,751
You'll be fine, right?

203
00:13:35,751 --> 00:13:37,644
Yes. I'll be totally fine.

204
00:13:37,644 --> 00:13:39,341
No sweat.

205
00:13:39,341 --> 00:13:40,938
Definitely no sweat.

206
00:13:40,938 --> 00:13:44,308
- I'm leaving then.
- Okay. Bye.

207
00:13:44,308 --> 00:13:47,262
- See you.
- Bye-bye. Come visit me.

208
00:13:47,262 --> 00:13:49,762
I'll have to check my schedule.

209
00:13:58,850 --> 00:14:00,267
I'm leaving now.

210
00:14:00,267 --> 00:14:01,399
You're leaving now?

211
00:14:01,399 --> 00:14:02,539
I'm leaving.

212
00:14:02,539 --> 00:14:04,547
Okay. Bye.

213
00:14:04,547 --> 00:14:06,010
Love you.

214
00:14:07,360 --> 00:14:10,422
