I have to travel 20 minutes?

215
00:14:12,604 --> 00:14:14,773
These are so damn heavy.

216
00:14:18,855 --> 00:14:20,757
Hi.

217
00:14:20,757 --> 00:14:23,082
My mom called and booked a room.

218
00:14:24,000 --> 00:14:26,601
Oh, you're moving in, right?

219
00:14:26,601 --> 00:14:27,739
Yes.

220
00:14:27,739 --> 00:14:29,058
Just a moment.

221
00:14:31,432 --> 00:14:32,401
The key.

222
00:14:32,401 --> 00:14:33,800
5th floor. Room 501.

223
00:14:33,800 --> 00:14:35,290
Your room will be to your left.

224
00:14:35,290 --> 00:14:38,279
No noise after 10 p.m. That's it.

225
00:14:39,147 --> 00:14:40,550
Thank you.

226
00:14:42,093 --> 00:14:43,854
Where's the elevator?

227
00:14:44,942 --> 00:14:46,382
There's none.

228
00:14:46,382 --> 00:14:48,166
Take the stairs.

229
00:14:48,166 --> 00:14:51,411
