give you an offering envelope.

254
00:16:56,744 --> 00:16:59,362
Thanks. I've received many envelopes this month.

255
00:16:59,362 --> 00:17:01,700
Please come again.

256
00:17:03,693 --> 00:17:05,415
Mom, you can leave it there. I'll do it.

257
00:17:05,415 --> 00:17:06,709
